OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784837925
OL,3,CSpecialist helicopter to be deployed
OL,4,Cto fight ongoing wildfire
OL,6,FA specialist firefighting helicopter
OL,7,Fwill be deployed to Rhinogydd on
OL,8,FFriday morning (24 July) to help
OL,9,Ftackle an ongoing wildfire.
OL,11,FThe announcement from Natural
OL,12,FResources Wales comes after the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment unsuccessfully tried to
OL,14,Fsource aerial support from the
OL,15,Fmilitary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
