FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784837925
OL,3,CSpecialist helicopter to be deployed
OL,4,Cto fight ongoing wildfire
OL,6,FOn Thursday afternoon a statement from
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Government it enquired with
OL,8,Fthe armed forces about using a
OL,9,Fhelicopter but there was "no
OL,10,Fappropriate aerial firefighting
OL,11,Fcapability based in the UK."
OL,13,FWelsh Government Minister Sian
OL,14,FGwenllian previously said: "No
OL,15,Fairborne firefighting capability is
OL,16,Fcurrently available for deployment
OL,17,Fanywhere in the UK to support these
OL,18,Fefforts."
OL,26,@uD@]sp
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
