OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784837925
OL,3,CSpecialist helicopter to be deployed
OL,4,Cto fight ongoing wildfire
OL,6,FThe lack of aerial supported prompted
OL,7,FWelsh Labour to call for the Senedd to
OL,8,Fbe recalled from its summer recess.
OL,10,FIn a statement posted on the afternoon
OL,11,Fof July 23, before the announcement of
OL,12,Fdeployed helicopter, Ken Skates MS,
OL,13,Fleader of the Welsh Labour Group,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I am deeply concerned about the
OL,15,Fwildfires across Wales.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784837925
OL,3,CSpecialist helicopter to be deployed
OL,4,Cto fight ongoing wildfire
OL,6,F"There is an urgent need for the
OL,7,FSenedd to meet in order for the
OL,8,Fgovernment to provide an update about
OL,9,Fthe response and give Members' the
OL,10,Fopportunity to represent their
OL,11,Fconstituents' views.
OL,13,F"The lack of aerial support is of
OL,14,Fgreat concern.
OL,16,F"My thoughts remain with everyone
OL,17,Faffected by the fires and I would like
OL,18,Fto thank the fire and rescue teams
OL,19,Facross Wales, who have been working
OL,20,Ftirelessly in very difficult
OL,21,Fcircumstances."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
