OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784837925
OL,3,CSpecialist helicopter to be deployed
OL,4,Cto fight ongoing wildfire
OL,6,FNatural Resources Wales said there has
OL,7,Fbeen "exceptional demand from wildfire
OL,8,Fincidents elsewhere in the UK."
OL,10,F"The helicopter will make a vital
OL,11,Fcontribution to the response, working
OL,12,Falongside the dedicated efforts of
OL,13,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Fcrews and our own teams, who have been
OL,15,Fsupporting the incident response on
OL,16,Fthe ground throughout."
OL,18,FHowever, NRW said the availability of
OL,19,Fthe helicopter will be "assessed in
OL,20,Fline with operational needs across
OL,21,FWales and the wider UK."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
